    <h2>Search Dynamic Images JavaScript Project Source Code </h2>
    <p>Step-1</p>
    <p> Create a index.html file </p>
    and add paste the below code in .html file
    <div class="code">
        <pre>
         
           &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;

            &lt;html&gt;


                &lt;head&gt;
            
           &lt;meta charset="utf-8"&gt;

          &lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"&gt;
  
        &lt;title&gt;Search images &lt;/title&gt;
 
